<head>
  <style>
    body{
        font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
         text-align: center;
      }
      .mailer{
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      img{
        width: 12rem;
        height auto;
        line-height: 1em; 
      }

      .header{
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1{
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        font-size: 2rem;
        line-height: 1em;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .invited{
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      }

      button{
        background: white;
        color: #585858!important;
        padding: 0.5em 2.3em;
        font-family: $sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        border-radius: 2px !important;
        -webkit-border-radius: 2px!important;
        -webkit-appearance: none!important;
        font-size: 1em;
        border: $border;
        border-color: #b9b9b9 !important;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      button:hover{
        border-color: #1B1B1B !important;
        box-shadow: none;
        outline: none;
      }

      p{
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      
  </style>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Heebo:100,300,400,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>


<body>
 <div class="mailer">
  <div class="header">
    <%= image_tag(attachments['logo.png'].url) %>
    <p class="invited">YOU'RE INVITED</p>  
    <h1>Welcome to Indielab.</h1>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p>
      Hello chosen one,
    </p> 
    <p>
      You've been invited to join Indielab - The Artist Playground. <br/>
      Indielab is a social-collaborative platform designed for creative expression. 
      Whether you create stories, pictures, music, video or you are just exploring interests; 
      Indielab is the place for you to play and be creative. 
    </p>
    <p> Do accept our invitation as we are excited to have you as part of our community. Together with you,
        we want to make Indielab the best platform for everyone to create, collaborate and be creative.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <a href="<%= accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @token) %>">
      <button> Accept Invitation </button>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p>Indielab is still in Beta so not everything will be perfect. <br/>
      But with your help, we can make Indielab as amazing as possible. <br/>
      Your feedback and suggestions are very welcomed and encouraged at beta@indielab.xyz
    </p>
  </div>
 </div>
</body>